<emphasis box="[948,1005,1452,1476]" italics="true" pageId="56" pageNumber="371">et al</emphasis>
. (2015)
</bibRefCitation>
this species described from 
<collectingCountry box="[831,897,1485,1508]" name="Brazil" pageId="56" pageNumber="371">Brazil</collectingCountry>
is present from the southern 
<collectingCountry box="[1279,1314,1485,1509]" name="United States of America" pageId="56" pageNumber="371">US</collectingCountry>
States of 
<collectingRegion box="[831,932,1517,1540]" country="United States of America" name="Alabama" pageId="56" pageNumber="371">Alabama</collectingRegion>
